N2  - The 1965 Eastern Meeting of The Institute of Management Sciences will be held on October 13?15, 1965 in the Sheraton Hotel, Rochester, New York. The invited and contributed papers on subjects in the theory and application of the management sciences are to be presented. In addition a half day colloquium on the subject of ?The Organizational Position of the Management Scientist? will be held. Also provided: ?Registration Information ?Committee members ?Program plan ?Preliminary program 1965 TIMS Eastern Meeting ?Announcement of the Dallas meeting, February 16?19, 1966 ?TIMS financial statement
